data.description: Welcome to your stunning single-story Perris home with NO HOA and SOLAR panels Paid off , offering you incredible VIEWS! As you step inside, you'll be immediately captivated by the light and bright open floor plan that opens up into the kitchen. The upgraded kitchen boasts granite countertops, custom tile backsplash, and window shutters . The master bathroom has dual sinks and a walk-in closet. The home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms. Enjoy the cozy backyard with Aluma wood patio, mounted tv and cabinets, vinyl fencing, and a relaxing low maintenance front yard . Located in a prime location close to shopping and the 215 Freeway, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your forever home!
